# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Agentium Backend Dockerfile (Privileged)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

FROM python:3.11-slim-bookworm

# Install system dependencies for host-level access
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    docker.io \
    openssh-client \
    procps \
    htop \
    tree \
    rsync \
    curl \
    wget \
    netcat-openbsd \
    iputils-ping \
    dnsutils \
    sysstat \
    iotop \
    nano \
    vim \
    git \
    build-essential \
    gcc \
    g++ \
    libpq-dev \
    python3-dev \
    libffi-dev \
    libssl-dev \
    # Xvfb and X11 libraries for pyautogui headless support
    xvfb \
    x11-utils \
    xauth \
    libx11-6 \
    libxext6 \
    libxrandr2 \
    libxi6 \
    libxtst6 \
    libxss1 \
    python3-tk \
    tk-dev \
    chromium \
    chromium-sandbox \
    fonts-liberation \
    fonts-noto-color-emoji \
    libnss3 \
    libatk1.0-0 \
    libatk-bridge2.0-0 \
    libcups2 \
    libdrm2 \
    libxcomposite1 \
    libxdamage1 \
    libxfixes3 \
    libxkbcommon0 \
    libgbm1 \
    libgtk-3-0 \
    libasound2 \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Install Node.js 22 LTS (via NodeSource — Bookworm apt version is too old)
RUN curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_22.x | bash - && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends nodejs && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Install Rust stable (rustup, installed globally so agentium user can use it)
ENV RUSTUP_HOME=/usr/local/rustup \
    CARGO_HOME=/usr/local/cargo \
    PATH=/usr/local/cargo/bin:$PATH
RUN curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSf https://sh.rustup.rs | \
    sh -s -- -y --no-modify-path --profile minimal --default-toolchain stable && \
    chmod -R a+w /usr/local/rustup /usr/local/cargo

# Create agentium user with root capabilities
RUN useradd -m -s /bin/bash -G sudo,docker agentium && \
    echo "agentium ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL" >> /etc/sudoers && \
    usermod -aG root agentium

WORKDIR /app

# Create necessary directories
RUN mkdir -p /app/backend /host /host_home /tmp/agentium_uploads/files /tmp/agentium_uploads/voice && \
    chmod -R 777 /tmp/agentium_uploads

# Install Python dependencies
COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install --upgrade pip setuptools wheel && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir --default-timeout=600 --retries=5 -r requirements.txt && \
    pip install --no-cache-dir nodriver

# Copy application code
COPY . .

# Set proper ownership
RUN chown -R agentium:agentium /app

USER agentium

ENV PYTHONPATH=/app \
    PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE=1 \
    PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 \
    HOST_ROOT_ACCESS=true \
    HOST_DOCKER_SOCKET=/var/run/docker.sock \
    HOST_FS_MOUNT=/host \
    HOST_HOME_MOUNT=/host_home \
    DISPLAY=:99 \
    XVFB_SCREEN=0 \
    XVFB_RESOLUTION=1920x1080x24 \
    CHROME_BIN=/usr/bin/chromium \
    RUSTUP_HOME=/usr/local/rustup \
    CARGO_HOME=/usr/local/cargo \
    PATH=/usr/local/cargo/bin:$PATH

EXPOSE 8000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=60s --retries=5 \
    CMD python -c "import http.client; conn = http.client.HTTPConnection('localhost', 8000); conn.request('GET', '/api/health'); exit(0 if conn.getresponse().status == 200 else 1)" || exit 1

COPY scripts/entrypoint.sh /entrypoint.sh

# Switch to root just to chmod, then back to agentium
USER root
RUN chmod +x /entrypoint.sh
USER agentium

ENTRYPOINT ["/entrypoint.sh"]
CMD ["uvicorn", "backend.main:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "8000"]